This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to automatically extract and summarize arguments from social media dialogs. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves similarity ranking and information retrieval, which are relevant to the categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
